---
to: prompt
description: RDF/OWL ontology generation prompt
vars:
  - name: domain
    type: string
    description: Domain description
  - name: requirements
    type: array
    description: Ontology requirements
    default: []
  - name: examples
    type: array
    description: Example patterns
    default: []
  - name: format
    type: string
    description: Output format
    default: "turtle"
---
Generate an RDF/OWL ontology for the following domain:

Domain: {{ domain }}

{% if requirements %}
Requirements:
{% for req in requirements %}
- {{ req }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if examples %}
Examples:
{% for example in examples %}
- {{ example }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if format %}
Output format: {{ format }}
{% endif %}

Please generate a complete RDF/OWL ontology in Turtle format with appropriate classes, properties, and relationships.
